---
<section id="about">
  <div class="sw">
    <div class="label">About</div>
    <h2 class="display">Rooted in <em>Bali</em>,<br />building for the world.</h2>
    <div class="about-layout rv">
      <div class="about-prose">
        <p>Most problems worth solving sit at the edge of disciplines — where the clinician hasn't met the engineer, where ancient knowledge hasn't met modern tooling, where a small island hasn't yet been taken seriously as a place that builds things.</p>
        <p>Whatever your expertise — use it on something that matters. The gaps are real, the tools are here, and the world doesn't need more observers.</p>
        <p>If your work touches any of mine, I'd like to hear from you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cards">
        <div class="acard"><div class="atitle">Edge of disciplines</div><div class="adesc">Where clinician meets engineer, where ancient meets modern.</div></div>
        <div class="acard"><div class="atitle">Use your expertise</div><div class="adesc">Whatever your domain — the work that matters is waiting at the edges.</div></div>
        <div class="acard"><div class="atitle">Bali builds</div><div class="adesc">A small island taken seriously as a place that makes things that matter.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="poleng" title="Poleng — the black-and-white checkered cloth of Balinese temples, worn to mark the balance of opposing forces (rwa bhineda)."></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about { background: var(--panel); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }

  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  .about-prose p {
    font-family: 'Literata', serif;
    font-size: var(--fs-lead); color: var(--dim); line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }
  .about-prose p strong { font-family: 'Fragment Mono', monospace; font-weight: 400; color: var(--paper); }

  .about-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 0.8rem; }
  .acard { flex: 1; }
  .acard {
    display: flex; gap: 0.9rem; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem; background: var(--void);
    border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 0;
  }
  .atitle { font-family: 'Fragment Mono', monospace; font-size: var(--fs-title); font-weight: 400; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
  .adesc  { font-size: var(--fs-body); color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.65; font-family: 'Literata', serif; }

  .poleng { margin-top: 3.5rem; }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .about-cards { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
